# Notifying all subscribers of a topic is not working properly · magicbell ...
created: 2024-11-02, last updated: 2025-05-26, [Read more](https://github.com/orgs/magicbell/discussions/213)

{
"broadcast": {
"title": "test",
"content": "test",
"category": "order_created",
"topic": "order:33098",
"recipients": [
{
"topic": "order:33098"
}
...
Hey @RuslanHryn please try this syntax for the topic recipients
```
"recipients": [
{
"topic": {
"subscribers": true
}
}
]
```

# Category
created: undefined, last updated: 2025-03-02, [Read more](https://www.magicbell.com/docs/primitives/category)

- Offer
...
When creating a broadcast, you can set a category in the
`broadcast.category` parameter.
A category must contain less than 256 characters and should not contain spaces.
```
"broadcast": {
"title": "Join the September webinar",
"category": "annoucement",
"recipients": [{
"topic": {
"subscribers": true
}]
